---
title: Double Falafel Couscous with Blistered Tomatoes, Olives and Feta
description: We're celebrating veggie night with this Middle Eastern-inspired couscous! Packed with oven-roasted falafel, blistered tomatoes, briny olives, feta and garlic-tossed carrots, this dish has checked off every flavour box!
